# Fluff Date: 2026-03-12 17:00:46
overview:<p>First fielded by the Collective of the Violet Crux, the RFL-3B replaces all standard weapons with a pair of binary laser cannons. The tonnage savings allowed engineers to double the heat sink capacity while eliminating the need for ammunition resupply. Even so, firing both cannons at full power in quick succession overwhelms the cooling systems, forcing most MechWarriors to keep their weapons in dazzle mode by default.</p>

capabilities:<p>Purpose-built for overwatch and fire support, best positioned on elevated terrain with clear sightlines. The twin blazers deliver punishing long-range firepower, and the absence of ammunition makes sustained operations possible without supply line concerns. Pilots must discipline themselves to stagger fire or default to dazzle mode, as full-power volleys from both arms will rapidly overwhelm even the expanded cooling system.</p>

